channel.title: I N F E X I S Scape Released [Most Professional PI]
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i51.tinypic.com/2mgqek7.jpg[/img][/center] [color=blue][b][center] (Previously released on Rune-Server.) I decided to release IS because I have not been working on anything for a long time now. I N F E X I S Scape.. with that I mean to make a old days feeling of RuneScape. What else it has is lots of details, with details I mean things such as.. be able to milk cows too have most npc spawns, that's just two examples of many. There's also some quests, in my opinion quests are important and good for the community.. here are some quests that are done.
The reason why I am releasing this is because I've moved onto Shard Revolution. By the way, this is a Project Insanity. Cook's Assistant Dragon Slayer Desert Treasure Horror from the Deep Recipe for DisasterImp Catcher Here are some more current features. Deposit Box Skill Interface 99 Level Interface Ship Traveling Genie Lamp/Event And here's some other features. Over 3200 NPC Spawns 50+ Shops Most NPC Drops
Okay, I've listed the most important features. More media will come soon.
Please keep the useless spamming & flaming out of this thread..
